Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I hadn't said anything until now, but I think this is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:11.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I only came to college to follow Mitsuo, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:16.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was always my plan, from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:25.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought there had to be some mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:31.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I tried to believe that, if I just waited there,\NKouko would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:40.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I wasn't there when Kouko returned, and we missed each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:45.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I felt like we would be separated forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:49.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But time marched on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:50.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and Kouko never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:03.96,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(281,296)}Paradise Lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:13.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aa yume no naka de aetara yueru ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:38.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ne, kanashimi dake sora kara maiochite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:46.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sonna koe ga kimi o ima demo kurushimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:50.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Soba de te o kasanetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:54.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kono omoi wa kienai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:02:02.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Futari me o awasetara hontou no koto yuenakutemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:06.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kimi no kotoba, dare yori mo sekai o terashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:10.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tonari de kimi wa "Sayonara wa ai shiteru" tte, sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:12.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sunao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watashi dake kodoku o utattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Egao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Arigato wa koi shiteru" tte sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:22.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ai no world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not actually a coincidence, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko told you to come, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Turn the car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't get any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tear me away from Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Turn the car around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:54.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you didn't chase after her, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You didn't chase Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even now, you're not telling me to let you see Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to face her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you're waiting for her to change her mind and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's awfully carefree of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:24.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what Kouko was thinking when she left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:28.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,However, there's something she suddenly asked me not long ago:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:35.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"When does a doctor prescribe anti-anxiety medication for a patient?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anti-anxiety medication...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She asked if it meant the patient was insecure and in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I nodded, and the conversation ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:52.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, have you been prescribed any medications?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:57.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't intend to draw any conclusions from your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:07.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just think it may be the reason\NKouko reconsidered her relationship with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did Kouko know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...that I was taking that medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.79,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(216,91)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.79,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(386,93)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}osteopathy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.79,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(127,229)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}You don't feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.79,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(127,247)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}giving up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay out here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you going to do "a little longer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going... to the convenience store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really? The convenience store, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fine, then. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I sort of know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda told me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You bought red-bean soup without looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.43,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(312,171)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Homemade Style{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.43,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(297,207)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Red-Bean Soup{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I heard about your fall from the bridge and your amnesia from Linda last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,when she was a first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just didn't say anything because it wasn't my place to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:19.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, I ate beef yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko's beef, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The way you said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:34.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda, that first year girl, and I wolfed down that beef like it was the best we'd ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Her parents must be amazing if she could afford to bring that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:43.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pretty important ones, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, what were you doing yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:49.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I... was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Honestly, I just wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:57.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't say you want to die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:57.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:10.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to disappear soon and be replaced by the former personality of Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anything I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:18.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's my normal, healthy state, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But it still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just keep falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:27.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda told me your accident was her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"How could I just abandon him like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I don't know what to do," she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:42.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I believe there's no such thing as a 20-year-old who knows what she should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:47.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You meet someone and then part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a natural part of the human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No one can promise they'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Life is suffering, pain, and misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:02.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Try to make it through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga Kouko's the one trying not to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko seems to have given up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:17.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She just told me it was time to call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:22.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:29.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The one who pretends to know everything never knows anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like apologizing to Linda, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:36.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:40.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Making light of others' pain, denying it, averting my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:44.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not even generous enough to share their burdens and help lighten them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:52.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You told me because you trust me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I ignored you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've come to hate myself in these last few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please don't think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:04.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You have no idea how much it helped to have you listen to me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I had stayed that way, I might really have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:09.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't be so thoughtless, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:16.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're the next to the next to the next to the next to the next person I like as much as Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In any case, go home and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:23.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then try talking to Kaga Kouko again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:34.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This special super sweet red-bean soup version is just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a proper conversation with Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to apologize for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:57.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ko-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just went off on you and I didn't even call you afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:10.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I left you after saying such mean things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:17.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The truth is, I got really worried a while after that and went back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were standing there forever, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I just couldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I sent my father to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:36.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You guys have first period, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, that sweater you're wearing is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're going to make static electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Banri, is your nose okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:49.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You seem totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been a little high-strung lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Actually, I've even been prescribed medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess I wasn't taking it properly, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:13.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But whatever happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,don't you feel like you'll be fine as long as you have Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here you go, Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have a free cup of coffee I poured just for the hell of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,without any special feelings behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't feel particularly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mine seems a little weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:46.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, your cup is super-specially rich with Banri's love for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wasn't Banri just telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:51.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Telling me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri and I broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I should let you all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're just back to being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you could keep treating us the way you have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you already forget what happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:26.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was long past time to end our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After calmly thinking about things,\NI decided I'd lost my feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So let's go back to being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I broke up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you'd like to change my mind, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:41.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then why did you talk to me this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told you, I wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Were you not listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was only being considerate because we're still friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you have a problem with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,it might be difficult for us to even be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We have the same lecture, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please, don't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:15.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know better than anyone how nonsensical she can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no way she's serious, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:24.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you won't let this go, I'll start avoiding all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}To class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Or is it too awkward for you to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In that case, I don't mind skipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't care about lectures anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't care about college anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This place, the people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The time I spend here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I really don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,2D-kun, you have a lecture, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to be alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But if anything comes up, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:32.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I can reach you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask Kaga-san something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I couldn't catch up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:02.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The other day, remember how I asked you to film me in your apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everything that happened after that was recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to fast forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't tell Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After this, you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then we went to Nana-senpai's room to eat beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:29.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san said she forgot something in your room and went back by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you're saying Kouko saw all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:38.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's explain it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:48.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll show her the video you filmed yesterday, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks, but it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you mean, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko already knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:59.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She knew I had amnesia before we started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:03.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko fell in love with me, even though I made no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She supported me plenty of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was such a burden to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't know how much pain I caused her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She did her best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:19.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't ask her to do any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does this mean it's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What about this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My name is Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:35.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk about the things that have happened to me up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Do whatever you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Erase it or use it for something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no way I could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really, do whatever you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That has meaning enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now we're both members of the Broken Hearts Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My brokenhearted Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:00.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're making a painful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is my face that painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:07.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can clearly tell you're forcing yourself to look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:11.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course, I only know because\NI've made the same face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:17.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to edit it together and present it at the school festival
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,as the diaries of a depressed co-ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? You're going to show it to Yana-san, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't mention who broke my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:31.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, Yana might figure it out anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I guess I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He might as well just figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you want to film my brokenhearted face, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can use me to accent your co-ed's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:47.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you say that, I really will film you and use the footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:52.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told you, all the footage you take of me using the Okamera belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:55.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello to everyone watching\NOka-chan's co-ed diaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was just dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel really awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:05.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what I should do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're even in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The club...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You suddenly got all gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That kind of stung.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, did I hit a painful spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was a fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you want, you can use it for the last scene of your film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?! You broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks like she got sick of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:41.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:47.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I want you to talk to Kouko like you did over the summer, when she misunderstood things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So she doesn't quit the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How can you be so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because she gave up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How can you accept that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:03.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is that all there was to your relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:06.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa, Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She dumped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gave up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Chase her and tell her you still love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I could do that, I would have done it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You hurt me first, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:35.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll never accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't understand how you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't you understand after the incident the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's over for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:52.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm just going to fall apart and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:58.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone can believe in the love of a person like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:59.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My disappearance is inevitable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have no future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm just a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, you're Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not the man you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who the hell is Tada Banri, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everyone calls me Tada Banri,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I have no clue who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What does that make me, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you can just give up like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,what am I supposed to do with my own feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you mean, your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You didn't accept me, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You didn't come to the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I did go, but I was too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why didn't you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I was late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How could you let that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:05.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I could, I'd go back and redo that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me redo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me do it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I can, I won't screw it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I swear I won't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you still have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There seems to be something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:33.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda and I have known each other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been keeping it from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:37.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:44.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been lying to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:49.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda and I have been together since high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Always in the same clubs and classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I loved Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to be with her forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:58.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I confessed my feelings to her on the day of our graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:05.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,while waiting for her answer, I got in an accident and was seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I lost all my memories up to that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:13.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My name, my parents, my home, my friends, Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everything disappeared from my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:21.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I forgot everything I ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The person who was reborn is the man before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:28.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for lying to you until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:34.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In fact, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why... Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,President, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.36,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(346,115)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}RESIGNATION{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:52.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:15.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Chigau yo mou, chigau tteba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aa, mada kizukanai no ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:24.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ni san jikan mo mae kara sono ude ni furetai noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sakebitai kimochi wa hora komaru hodo aru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:44.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Doushite doushite chittomo aa satotte kurenai no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ne hontou ni hontou ni watashi ni koi shiteru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:57.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kosabayui kotoba wa iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Han eikyuuteki ni ai shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gosen-nen go nado kyoumi wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:07.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watashi endless de wa nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Itsuka wa shinu no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:17.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Eien ni ai shiteru yo" nante yuwaretemo ureshikunai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mazu wa watashi o shinu made
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:25.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ai suru koto dake o kangaete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:40.94,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,409)}Last Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:29.00,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(141,371)}Sorry, Banri. You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:31.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(137,371)}But hair that falls out can't go back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.34,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(105,368)}The hair on a man's head affects his future!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.21,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(235,371)}There's no fixing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:37.48,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(240,371)}Why did you pull it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:38.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(262,371)}Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:40.81,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(250,371)}And you're scary...
